-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰里·哈里森和阿德里安·贝卢。图片来源：迈克尔·温特罗布" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jerry-Harrison-and-Adrian-Belew.-Credit-Michael-Weintrob-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Talking-Heads">Talking Heads</a>的 Jerry Harrison 和<a href="/artists/King-Crimson">King Crimson</a>的 Adrian Belew 宣布了他们的 2025 年“Remain In Light”英国和欧洲巡演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/talking-heads-every-album-ranked-in-order-of-greatness-3486762">Talking Heads：每张专辑按伟大程度排列</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>在为期五场的演出中，哈里森和贝卢将从 5 月 18 日在斯德哥尔摩的演出开始，穿越欧盟和英国。从那里开始，二人组将在奥斯陆、哥本哈根、科隆、华沙和卢森堡等城市停留，然后再前往其他城市。前往英国，经停曼彻斯特和伍尔弗汉普顿。巡演将于 6 月 7 日在伦敦结束。</p><p>这次巡演被命名为“Remain In Light”，这也是 Talking Heads 1980 年唱片的标题。它是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-eno">布莱恩·伊诺 (Brian Eno)</a>制作的乐队的第三张也是最后一张专辑，并且还邀请了许多其他音乐家为这张唱片做出贡献，其中包括弹吉他的贝卢 (Belew)。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，哈里森和贝卢将与他们的全明星伴奏乐队一起表演 Talking Heads 的经典歌曲，如《一生一次》、《心理杀手》、《带我去河》以及选自他们各自传奇的独奏生涯。</p><p> Cool Cool Cool 将在所有日期担任特邀嘉宾。门票将于当地时间本周五（12 月 6 日）上午 10 点开始公开发售。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fjerry-harrison-of-talking-heads-tickets%2Fartist%2F2035672" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票并查看下面的完整日期列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDHtbj0Nh9X/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.0