 Fuse ODG 以“We Know It's Christmas”回击 Band Aid 单曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/fuse-odg-hits-back-at-band-aid-single-with-we-know-its-christmas-3818462?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fuse- odg 在创可贴单曲《we-know-its-christmas》中回归Anagricel DuranTue, 03 Dec 2024 20:10:01 +0000 Music NewsNewsChristmasPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3818462 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="融合 ODG 和鲍勃·格尔多夫。图片来源：Joseph Okpako 和 Lorne Thomson，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是关于赋权、自豪感，并向世界展示非洲的故事不仅仅是贫困和援助”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fuse-odg-hits-back-at-band-aid-single-with-we-know-its-christmas-3818462">Fuse ODG 凭借《We Know It&#39;s Christmas》反击 Band Aid 单曲，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="融合 ODG 和鲍勃·格尔多夫。图片来源：Joseph Okpako 和 Lorne Thomson，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fuse-ODG-and-Bob-Geldof.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Fuse ODG 回击了 Band Aid 翻拍的《Do They Know It&#39;s Christmas?》与单曲“我们知道这是圣诞节”。</p><p>这位英国加纳歌手最近批评了对非洲的外国援助，他透露，他的单曲“不仅仅是一首歌”，而是“一份声明”。这首歌的随附视频以这位格莱美奖获奖音乐家出现在英国<em>独立电视台《早安英国》</em>的片段开头，其中他说“非洲问题需要由非洲人来解决”。</p><p>在视频的描述中，这位歌手分享道：“《We Know It&#39;s Christmas》是对 1984 年 Band Aid 单曲《Do They Know It&#39;s Christmas?》的直接反驳。”富斯认为，这延续了对非洲过时的负面刻板印象，将非洲大陆仅仅描绘成一个贫穷和饥荒的地方。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Fuse ODG - 我们知道这是圣诞节（创可贴回复）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3np_fs-t6lY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “该发布日期也标志着 Fuse ODG 拒绝参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">Bob Geldof 爵士</a>领导的 2014 年 Band Aid 项目改造邀请而成为全球头条新闻的 10 周年。这位音乐家的决定引发了广泛的争论，但富斯立场坚定，坚称非洲的声音应该站在讲述自己故事的最前沿。”</p><p> “这反映了我们从哪里来，要去哪里，”Fuse 补充道。 “十年前，我表明立场，因为我相信现在是非洲人讲述自己的故事并重新定义叙事的时候了。这首歌是对这一转变的庆祝。我们不再等待施舍；我们正在建设我们自己的未来。这是关于赋权、自豪感，并向世界展示非洲的故事不仅仅是贫困和援助。”</p><p> Fuse 的这首歌曲是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a>表示自己的声音被用于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-star-2024-ulimate-mix-of-band-aids-do-they-know-its-christmas-coming-later-this-month-3812230">“2024 Ultimate Mix”版本的“Do They Know It&#39;s Christmas?”</a>之后发布的。未经许可。</p><p>这首歌曲的新混音由 Trevor Horn 制作，汇集了该歌曲三个版本的所有声音，录制于 1984 年、2004 年和 2014 年。如果我有选择的话，我会恭敬地拒绝使用我的声音。”希兰在 Instagram Stories 上写道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="创可贴 - 他们知道今天是圣诞节吗？ （官方视频）[4K]" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RH-xd5bPKTA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="创可贴 30 - 他们知道今天是圣诞节吗？ (2014)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-w7jyVHocTk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “十年过去了，我对与此相关的叙述的理解已经改变，@fuseodg 雄辩地解释了这一点，”他继续说道。 “这只是我个人的立场，我希望这是一个前瞻性的立场。爱所有的x。”</p><p>在更新中，Sheeran 还分享了 Fuse ODG 发布的帖子的屏幕截图（他在声明中提到了 Fuse ODG），Fuse ODG 解释了为什么<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-1301-1220230">他拒绝为 2014 版本做出贡献的提议。</a></p><p>最初，这首慈善单曲是由 Geldof 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/midge-ure">Midge Ure</a>策划的，目的是为埃塞俄比亚的饥荒筹集资金。它在第一周就售出了一百万张，并且成为当时英国排行榜历史上销售最快的单曲。</p><p>格尔多夫在接受<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/bob-geldof-do-they-know-its-christmas-charity-song-1235840783/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-says-hell-have-a-talk-with-ed-sheeran-about-band-aid-dispute-3817164">谈到了他对希兰立场的看法，并表示他正在寻求与希兰进行讨论</a>。</p><p>在发表评论后，一位接近 Band Aid 的消息人士告诉<em>NME</em> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-has-put-a-call-in-to-ed-sheeran-over-band-aid-single-controversy-theyll-work-it-out-3814078">Geldof 已就此事亲自联系了 Sheeran</a> ，这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boomtown-rats">Boomtown Rats</a>主唱后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-responds-to-ed-sheerans-band-aid-comments-this-little-pop-song-has-kept-millions-of-people-alive-3815381">在接受采访时为这首单曲进行了辩护</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDFsJN7O5Wz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41