oks">kooks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lathums">lathums</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">湿腿都</a>将出现。其他行为包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-webster">Jamie Webster</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/twin-atlantic">Twin Atlantic</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-bugg">Jake Bugg</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sigrid">Sigrid</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underworld">Underworld</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Shed Seven</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nina-nesbitt">Nina Nesbitt</a> 。</p><p>还将参加比赛的是Calum Bowie，Royston Club，Tanner Adell， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alessi-rose">Alessi Rose</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biig-piig">Biig Piig</a> ，Amble，Amble，James Marriott， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ks">K Q</a> ，Kerr Mercer， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nieve-ella">Nieve Ella</a>和Rianne Downey，将在宣布的情况下宣布更多事件。 </p><figure id="attachment_3818468" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3818468" style="width: 1081px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3818468" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup.jpg" alt="TRNSMT 2025阵容" width="1081" height="1351" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup.jpg 1081w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/TRNSMT-Lineup-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1081px) 100vw, 1081px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3818468" class="wp-caption-text"> TRNSMT 2025阵容。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>节日总监杰夫·埃利斯（Geoff Ellis）说：“在2024年售罄的销售纪录之后，我们迫不及待地想让所有人回到令人难以置信的现场音